widgets_values: Adjusting the Motion Scale can lead to increased motion, though it may occasionally produce unpredictable outcomes. A range between 1.0 and 1.4 generally works well.

To better preserve the original image style, increase the weights of ipadapters or switch to the ipadapter Plus model in the Unified Loader node. Lowering the "end_at" setting enhances the influence of the QRcode Controlnet and AnimateDiff on motion control.

Maintain the default batch_size unless you are certain about the adjustments required. IPAdapter attention mask values aren't modular and need to be hand adjusted when changing the batch size.
This should be a black and white looping animation. Preferably 12/24/48 frame length in square resolution so it combines nicely with ipadapters attention mask.
